cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper deals with multilingual entity reference resolution, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves unsupervised learning and similarity detection, which are relevant to sub-categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper mentions boosting the probability of finding true friends, which could be related to sub-category cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
